{"tid":1340840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立香港自衛隊第一步：成立「香港民眾保安公司」","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T01:08:25.000Z","uid":274879,"like":170,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"88edec7891f9e1a22d0c17819a86438c1c480cc7","tid":1340840,"uid":274879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"(朋友FB講)<br />\n<br />\n今晚元朗警察唔救人，而民間自己持有自衛武器一定非法，要合法持有自衛武力只有「保安」一途。好似每次集會有First Aider救人咁，點解唔可以有間正牌保安公司，會提供保護民眾嘅保安服務？D明星富豪都有自己武裝保安，我覺得我d出黎行駛公民權利嘅朋友，而家呢個時勢比佢地仲需要武力保護。<br />\n<br />\n成立保安公司：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/links/sgsia/howto-scl.htm?fbclid=IwAR0aTiGF11QSHdqGM2vikZKx6fJmMd4D0rAa7FTjTVUl4ZcdHSP9ysXmzL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sb.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Flinks%2Fsgsia%2Fhowto-scl.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0aTiGF11QSHdqGM2vikZKx6fJmMd4D0rAa7FTjTVUl4ZcdHSP9ysXmzL8&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=000be07a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/links/sgsia/howto-scl.htm?fbclid=IwAR0aTiGF11QSHdqGM2vikZKx6fJmMd4D0rAa7FTjTVUl4ZcdHSP9ysXmzL8</a>"},{"pid":"01c0806fd47a2b7787927429f1ed0fa7b4c42c1b","tid":1340840,"uid":92264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！"},{"pid":"5da6b34e76eb9302b271ab25ac4008d8c704f42e","tid":1340840,"uid":132611,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"推,要集資開聲"},{"pid":"16028d88f7289d7db90dfce6e84dd6d6c52a77eb","tid":1340840,"uid":31758,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"牌照課的地址：<br />\n香港灣仔 <br />\n軍器廠街1號 <br />\n警察總部 <br />\n警政大樓12樓<br />\n<br />\n電話號碼： <br />\n2860 6543<br />\n<br />\n你覺得會批？"},{"pid":"871fce3014dcde3f2b8c3c4b0d0d434b49d6e504","tid":1340840,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9ddd42323168646015b89be8665a67ee7035a877","tid":1340840,"uid":18